csExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_7421166\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_7421166\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juni 29, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104hnz1719661363571.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hnz1719661363571.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hnz1719661363571.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"vay1665702601641\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $occcheck\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"vay1665702601641___occcheck_277582\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return or set the requirement for checking an occurrence.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"vay1665702601641__topic_d86852e1_d86853e1_d86854e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vay1665702601641__p_d86855e1_d86856e1_d86857e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occcheck</span> { <code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code> }</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vay1665702601641__p_d86858e1_d86859e1_d86860e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occcheck</span> { <code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code> } <code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Expression</var>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vay1665702601641__p_d86861e1_d86862e1_d86863e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">set</span> | <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">reset</span>\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occcheck</span> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code> }</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vay1665702601641__topic_d57777e1_d57778e1_d57779e1_d57780e1_d57781e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d552758e119\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"vay1665702601641__table_d9233e1_d9234e1_d9235e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vay1665702601641__table_d9233e1_d9234e1_d9235e1__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vay1665702601641__table_d9233e1_d9234e1_d9235e1__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vay1665702601641__table_d9233e1_d9234e1_d9235e1__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vay1665702601641__table_d9233e1_d9234e1_d9235e1__entry__1\">\n                        Entity\n                     </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vay1665702601641__table_d9233e1_d9234e1_d9235e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vay1665702601641__table_d9233e1_d9234e1_d9235e1__entry__3\">\n Entity name. If omitted, the current entity is used.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vay1665702601641__table_d9233e1_d9234e1_d9235e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Expression</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vay1665702601641__table_d9233e1_d9234e1_d9235e1__entry__2\">\n Boolean\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vay1665702601641__table_d9233e1_d9234e1_d9235e1__entry__3\">\n Expression that evaluates to a boolean value, explicitly setting the value of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occcheck</span>. When <var class=\"keyword varname\">Expression</var> evaluates to a nonzero value, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occcheck</span> becomes 1.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vay1665702601641__topic_d57782e1_d57783e1_d57784e1_d57785e1_d57786e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d552758e194\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"vay1665702601641__table_d9236e1_d9237e1_d9238e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occcheck</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vay1665702601641__table_d9236e1_d9237e1_d9238e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vay1665702601641__table_d9236e1_d9237e1_d9238e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Meaning</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vay1665702601641__table_d9236e1_d9237e1_d9238e1__entry__1\">\n 0\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vay1665702601641__table_d9236e1_d9237e1_d9238e1__entry__2\">\n Occurrence checking is not enabled.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vay1665702601641__table_d9236e1_d9237e1_d9238e1__entry__1\">\n 1\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vay1665702601641__table_d9236e1_d9237e1_d9238e1__entry__2\">\n Occurrence checking is currently enabled.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vay1665702601641__p_d86870e1_d86871e1_d86872e1\">When <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occcheck</span> is used as the target of an assignment, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span> is set:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"vay1665702601641__table_d9239e1_d9240e1_d9241e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 3. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vay1665702601641__table_d9239e1_d9240e1_d9241e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vay1665702601641__table_d9239e1_d9240e1_d9241e1__entry__2\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vay1665702601641__table_d9239e1_d9240e1_d9241e1__entry__1\">\n \"\"\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vay1665702601641__table_d9239e1_d9240e1_d9241e1__entry__2\">\n Occurrence checking could not be enabled. This usually means that <var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var> is not present or does not exist.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vay1665702601641__table_d9239e1_d9240e1_d9241e1__entry__1\">\n 1\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vay1665702601641__table_d9239e1_d9240e1_d9241e1__entry__2\">\n Occurrence checking was successfully enabled.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vay1665702601641__topic_d57787e1_d57788e1_d57789e1_d57790e1_d57791e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d552758e313\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vay1665702601641__d6417e20\">Allowed in all component types, except self-contained Reports.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vay1665702601641__topic_d57792e1_d57793e1_d57794e1_d57795e1_d57796e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d552758e323\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vay1665702601641__p_d86882e1_d86883e1_d86884e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occcheck</span> indicates whether the current occurrence of <var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var> is to be validated the next time that validation can occur.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vay1665702601641__p_d86885e1_d86886e1_d86887e1\">If <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occcheck</span> indicates that validation is demanded, validation is performed regardless of whether validation is actually required. (Validation is required when both <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occmod</span> and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occvalidation</span> are 1, indicating that the occurrence has been modified, but has not yet been validated.)</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vay1665702601641__p_d86888e1_d86889e1_d86890e1\">Validation can occur when:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vay1665702601641__li_d35009e1_d35010e1_d35011e1\">The user leaves the occurrence (for example, with ^NEXT_OCC or a mouse click)\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vay1665702601641__li_d35012e1_d35013e1_d35014e1\">An explicit validation statement is encountered (for example, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">validateocc</span>)\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vay1665702601641__li_d35015e1_d35016e1_d35017e1\">A <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">store</span> statement is encountered.\n </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vay1665702601641__p_d86891e1_d86892e1_d86893e1\">Validation includes syntax checks for each field in the entity, activation of the validate trigger, and in forms only, activation of the leaveModified trigger. After validation completes, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occcheck</span> is set to 0.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vay1665702601641__p_d86894e1_d86895e1_d86896e1\">You can also set the value of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occcheck</span> as a ProcScript assignment. Set <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occcheck</span> to 1 to require checking for the specified entity; set it to 0 to let Uniface take responsibility for validation. For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$occcheck=!$occcheck</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vay1665702601641__section_ftl_s2y_wbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d552758e390\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occcheck</span></h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following example shows how to use this function in the getFocus\n            trigger:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"vay1665702601641__pre_esc_t2y_wbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger getFocus ; of Entity\n set $occcheck(CUSTOMER)\nend ; getFocus\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">This use of the function <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occcheck</span> causes the\n            leaveModified trigger in the form to behave like a loseFocus trigger.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lrk1665702576500.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Validate</a><p>Determines whether the valerr data processing attribute is added for the selected entity node in the DTD tree. This attribute holds the occurrence or field validation error (depending on whether the selected item is an entity or field). Valid values are True or False (default).</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jwi1665702576586.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>validatefield</a><p>Validate a field of the current occurrence.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fdp1665702576817.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>validatekey</a><p>Validate a key of the current occurrence.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bwv1665702576896.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>validateocc</a><p>Validate an occurrence.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/swr1665702599962.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$fieldcheck</a><p>Return or set the requirement for field validation.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ogw1665702600188.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$fieldendmod</a><p>Return the modification status of a field when the field is exited.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rjy1665702601052.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$fieldmod</a><p>Return the modification status of a field.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/flp1665702599747.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$keycheck</a><p>Indicate whether a specified primary or candidate key should be validated.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nij1665702601782.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$keymod</a><p>Return a value indicating whether the specified key has been modified.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/eai1665702600334.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$occmod</a><p>Return the modification status of an occurrence.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fpz1719812992669.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$occvalidation</a><p>Check whether an occurrence requires validation.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xmm1665702603717.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>trigger leaveModified</a><p>Trigger that handles processing after the user moves to another occurrence in a form, after having modified the original occurrence.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/iwi1665702603846.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>trigger validate (Entity)</a><p>System trigger for validating entity occurrences.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7421166\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7421166\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$occcheck Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juni 29, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $occcheck Return or set the requirement for checking an occurrence. $occcheck { ( Entity ) } $occcheck { ( Entity ) } = Expression set | reset $occcheck { ( Entity ) } Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description Entity String Entity name. If omitted, the current entity is used. Expression Boolean Expression that evaluates to a boolean value, explicitly setting the value of $occcheck . When Expression evaluates to a nonzero value, $occcheck becomes 1. Return Values Table 2. Values returned in $occcheck Value Meaning 0 Occurrence checking is not enabled. 1 Occurrence checking is currently enabled. When $occcheck is used as the target of an assignment, $status is set: Table 3. Values returned in $status Value Meaning \"\" Occurrence checking could not be enabled. This usually means that Entity is not present or does not exist. 1 Occurrence checking was successfully enabled. Use Allowed in all component types, except self-contained Reports. Description $occcheck indicates whether the current occurrence of Entity is to be validated the next time that validation can occur. If $occcheck indicates that validation is demanded, validation is performed regardless of whether validation is actually required. (Validation is required when both $occmod and $occvalidation are 1, indicating that the occurrence has been modified, but has not yet been validated.) Validation can occur when: The user leaves the occurrence (for example, with ^NEXT_OCC or a mouse click) An explicit validation statement is encountered (for example, validateocc ) A store statement is encountered. Validation includes syntax checks for each field in the entity, activation of the validate trigger, and in forms only, activation of the leaveModified trigger. After validation completes, $occcheck is set to 0. You can also set the value of $occcheck as a ProcScript assignment. Set $occcheck to 1 to require checking for the specified entity; set it to 0 to let Uniface take responsibility for validation. For example: $occcheck=!$occcheck Copy Example: Using $occcheck The following example shows how to use this function in the getFocus trigger: trigger getFocus ; of Entity set $occcheck(CUSTOMER) end ; getFocus Copy This use of the function $occcheck causes the leaveModified trigger in the form to behave like a loseFocus trigger. Related Links Validate Determines whether the valerr data processing attribute is added for the selected entity node in the DTD tree. This attribute holds the occurrence or field validation error (depending on whether the selected item is an entity or field). Valid values are True or False (default). validatefield Validate a field of the current occurrence. validatekey Validate a key of the current occurrence. validateocc Validate an occurrence. $fieldcheck Return or set the requirement for field validation. $fieldendmod Return the modification status of a field when the field is exited. $fieldmod Return the modification status of a field. $keycheck Indicate whether a specified primary or candidate key should be validated. $keymod Return a value indicating whether the specified key has been modified. $occmod Return the modification status of an occurrence. $occvalidation Check whether an occurrence requires validation. trigger leaveModified Trigger that handles processing after the user moves to another occurrence in a form, after having modified the original occurrence. trigger validate (Entity) System trigger for validating entity occurrences. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}